---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="RecVerseShop — Catalog"
  description="A small, focused catalog. No checkout: express interest, clarify scope, and define the next sensible step."
>
  <main class="landing-page landing-page--shop">
    <section class="hero section">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <p class="eyebrow">RecVerseShop</p>
          <h1>A small, focused catalog instead of generic fixed packages</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            No traditional checkout, no blind instant purchase. You express interest, we briefly review
            context, feasibility, and sensible scope — and define the next step from there.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#catalog">View catalog</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/en/contact/?topic=Initial%20Consultation">Request an initial consultation</a>
          </div>

          <ul class="hero-points" aria-label="Principles">
            <li>No overengineering</li>
            <li>Clear scope definition</li>
            <li>Realistic implementation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-card">
          <div class="card-glow"></div>
          <div class="hero-panel">
            <p class="panel-label">How the shop works</p>
            <h2>Interest first. Execution only when it genuinely makes sense.</h2>
            <p>
              The offers in this catalog are intentionally compact. The goal is not to sell as much
              as possible, but to structure suitable entry points, reviews, and project starts in a clean way.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-alt">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="section-kicker">Process</p>
        <h2>What happens after an inquiry</h2>

        <div class="steps-grid">
          <article class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">01</div>
            <h3>Express interest</h3>
            <p>
              You choose a suitable topic or package and send a short inquiry.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">02</div>
            <h3>Review scope</h3>
            <p>
              We clarify what is sensible, realistic, and proportionate in your situation.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">03</div>
            <h3>Define the next step</h3>
            <p>
              You receive a concrete assessment instead of a mismatched standard sale.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="catalog">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="section-kicker">Catalog</p>
        <h2>Compact offers with a clear focus</h2>
        <p class="body-large section-intro">
          The offers below are designed as structured entry points. Pricing, scope, and depth depend
          on your starting point, complexity, and the outcome you are aiming for.
        </p>

        <div class="shop-grid">
          <article class="shop-card">
            <div class="shop-card-head">
              <span class="shop-tag">Review</span>
              <h3>Website Privacy Check</h3>
            </div>

            <p class="shop-price">SMEs: CHF 380 · Private: CHF 100</p>

            <p>
              A compact review of common website privacy weaknesses: forms, transparency,
              baseline notices, and obvious operational risks.
            </p>

            <ul class="shop-list">
              <li>Focus on practical weaknesses</li>
              <li>Suitable for SMEs and private projects</li>
              <li>No overloaded full-scale audit</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="shop-actions">
              <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/contact/?topic=Website%20Privacy%20Check&package=SME">For SMEs</a>
              <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/en/contact/?topic=Website%20Privacy%20Check&package=Private">For private use</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="shop-card">
            <div class="shop-card-head">
              <span class="shop-tag">MVP</span>
              <h3>AI MVP Sprint</h3>
            </div>

            <p class="shop-price">From use case to a clearly defined MVP start</p>

            <p>
              A structured path from an initial idea to a realistically scoped MVP or PoC —
              with clear boundaries, sensible limitations, and a clean next step.
            </p>

            <ul class="shop-list">
              <li>Refine the use case</li>
              <li>Reduce scope and risk</li>
              <li>Prepare the MVP / PoC realistically</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="shop-actions">
              <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/contact/?topic=AI%20MVP%20/%20PoC&package=AI%20MVP%20Sprint">Express interest</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="shop-card">
            <div class="shop-card-head">
              <span class="shop-tag">Enablement</span>
              <h3>ERP &amp; AI Enablement</h3>
            </div>

            <p class="shop-price">Use case, risks, pilot plan</p>

            <p>
              Assessment of AI potential in ERP and IT contexts with a focus on interfaces,
              feasibility, operational risks, and a sound pilot or implementation path.
            </p>

            <ul class="shop-list">
              <li>Use case selection with prioritization</li>
              <li>Interface and risk assessment</li>
              <li>A realistic next project stage</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="shop-actions">
              <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/contact/?topic=ERP%20/%20IT%20Project%20Management&module=ERP%20%26%20AI%20Enablement">Express interest</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="shop-card">
            <div class="shop-card-head">
              <span class="shop-tag">Web</span>
              <h3>Website Renewal / SEO Foundation</h3>
            </div>

            <p class="shop-price">Modernization with a focus on trust and baseline performance</p>

            <p>
              Redesign or structural improvement of your website with a focus on clarity,
              readability, trust, and technically sound SEO fundamentals.
            </p>

            <ul class="shop-list">
              <li>Redesign with clearer user guidance</li>
              <li>Baseline SEO instead of SEO overpromising</li>
              <li>Improved trust and structure</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="shop-actions">
              <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/contact/?topic=Website%20Renewal%20/%20SEO&package=Website%20Renewal%20/%20SEO%20Foundation">Express interest</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-alt">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="section-kicker">Positioning</p>
        <h2>What this shop is deliberately not</h2>

        <div class="trust-grid">
          <article class="trust-card">
            <h3>Not a mass-market checkout</h3>
            <p>
              These offers are not anonymous one-click purchases. They are structured entry points for meaningful work.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="trust-card">
            <h3>Not blind selling</h3>
            <p>
              Not every package fits every situation. That is why scope is reviewed first.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="trust-card">
            <h3>No unrealistic promises</h3>
            <p>
              The focus is on clear next steps, not inflated performance claims.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section cta-section">
      <div class="container cta-box">
        <div>
          <p class="section-kicker">Next step</p>
          <h2>Have you found a topic that fits?</h2>
          <p class="body-large">
            Then express your interest. We will briefly review whether the format fits
            and what the most sensible next step looks like.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-actions">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/en/contact/?topic=Initial%20Consultation">Start your inquiry</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/en/services/">View services</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <style>
    .landing-page--shop .steps-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .landing-page--shop .trust-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .landing-page--shop .shop-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .landing-page--shop .shop-card {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      background: var(--rv-bg-soft);
      border: 1px solid var(--rv-border);
      border-radius: var(--rv-radius);
      box-shadow: var(--rv-shadow);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      padding: 1.35rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.7rem;
      min-height: 100%;
    }

    .landing-page--shop .shop-card-head {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.45rem;
    }

    .landing-page--shop .shop-card h3 {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .landing-page--shop .shop-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--rv-accent);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .landing-page--shop .shop-price {
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--rv-text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .landing-page--shop .shop-card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--rv-text-soft);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .landing-page--shop .shop-list {
      margin: 0.15rem 0 0;
      padding-left: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--rv-text-soft);
    }

    .landing-page--shop .shop-list li {
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }

    .landing-page--shop .shop-actions {
      margin-top: auto;
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      padding-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .landing-page--shop .shop-actions .btn,
    .landing-page--shop .shop-actions .btn:visited {
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .landing-page--shop .shop-actions .btn-primary,
    .landing-page--shop .shop-actions .btn-primary:visited {
      color: #071018;
    }

    .landing-page--shop .shop-actions .btn-secondary,
    .landing-page--shop .shop-actions .btn-secondary:visited {
      color: var(--rv-text);
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .landing-page--shop .shop-grid,
      .landing-page--shop .steps-grid,
      .landing-page--shop .trust-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .landing-page--shop .shop-actions {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: stretch;
      }

      .landing-page--shop .shop-actions .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>